Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真少见啊波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还有两站就到池袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:54.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你闻到叶香的味道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.56,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只是心血来潮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\pos(450.668,1050.001)}抱歉 抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.03,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,疼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\pos(1336.001,1050.001)}没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\pos(1221.333,1050.001)}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\pos(917.332,99.999)}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.85,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前面有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,动物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,…的玩偶装？
