Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不进攻过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个胖墩是草饼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得不是 但是小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.37,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,别担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.61,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我们就是出去转一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.80,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,搞清楚原因就立刻回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.36,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,大概两个小时就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.60,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,最多也就两周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,认错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:11.57,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,你是静留吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？没认错人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.18,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,哦是静留啾噜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:17.40,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,荣作、秀坊 这是我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.01,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,那是静留咻噼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:19.81,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,哦是真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:20.80,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,真的是她啁！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留家的爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还有没回来的消防队的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.33,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,是玲实和晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.56,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,所以你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.04,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,你是抚子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这是波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.26,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,哦 抚子你还是这么正经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.01,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,久疏问候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,适可而止啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.36,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,静留 你长大了好多啾噜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是爸爸你变小了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:45.61,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,这个笑话好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,才不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叔叔 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也长高了不少吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.09,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.65,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,抚子也变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.76,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,晶你……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.72,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,晶就没什么变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.02,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,波奇现在看比之前可怕多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.58,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,大到吓着我了啾噜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:05.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你看你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是我们开过来的！是不是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.03,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,真有你的 开着这么威风的东西来显摆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么一点都不惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.96,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,毕竟周围都这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.84,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,就这种程度可吓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对了 妈妈让我遇上你之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:20.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就告诉你「别犯傻了早点回来」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.50,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,吓了一大跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:22.76,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,她生气了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,失望透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.73,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:25.94,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,她那样更可怕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:26.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谁管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.08,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我就和她说出去瞅一眼的啾噜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可已经两年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.05,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,但是但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.37,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我也送过信回去哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那种东西不算信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.601\b0\fs90\fnComic Sans MS\c&H485250&\frz7.103\fax0.06\pos(952.501,504)}我要再晚些回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:35.18,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,妈妈都无语了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.58,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,吾野的大家都还好吗咻噼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,政晴先生经常展露攻击性就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.37,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,阿政这人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.52,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,以前就有这个毛病了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.77,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,就连我们都偶尔会受到本能的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.27,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,更不用说阿政了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以你们之前在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:52.85,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.06,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,身体和人力工程车都快坏了啾噜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以说刚才开始你就在啾噜啾噜什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还有怎么变得这么圆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:05:59.76,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,啊 你注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那当然了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.45,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:02.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我都在尽量无视你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但你停都不停就更恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:07.85,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,嘴子好臭啊！别让我在你朋友旁边发火！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.72,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,千仓先生 没办法啁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.97,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,实际上大叔说「啾噜」或者「咻噼」就是很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.00,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我们…是被人变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,被谁变的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.42,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,一群椎名町的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.71,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我们在路上遇到了奇怪的老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.62,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,他说「池袋真是不得了了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.37,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我们准备去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.14,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,然后就和椎名町的人干了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.33,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎么回事 就变可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你输了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.35,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,才没输啾噜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别说「啾噜」了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.50,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,如果我不是动物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.37,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,就能靠吾野柔术轻松取胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.88,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我可没说谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.04,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我干掉了一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.36,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,你看！战利品！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,贝雷帽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.21,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,他们每个人都戴着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:45.76,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,你要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.47,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:47.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.20,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,哦！给你给你 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.22,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,乱步 格瓦拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.46,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,此乃叛逆与颓废之证！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.10,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,那你们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.77,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,是来找我们的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们是去池袋带叶香回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.29,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,叶香？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:02.97,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,千仓先生 那果然是叶香咻噼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:03.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们遇到她了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.21,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我们是在椎名町遇到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.68,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,但是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.42,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,她看上去和我喝酒晚归时的你妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我怎么知道是什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:22.43,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.88,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,之后就是一场闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你觉得她还在椎名町吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.19,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说到底真的是叶香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.73,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,你要真这么说的话…也许不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是怎样啦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.01,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我怎么知道啾噜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,都说了别再「啾噜」了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.44,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.46,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你有注意到什么在意的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.52,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我想起来了 她头发变得很长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她头发本来就长！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.68,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,可是 都长到地面了哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:49.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就不可能是叶香了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香会给自己剪发的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她很拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.25,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,真的麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你们的手够不到 没办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.15,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 是善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我完全没听到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不愧是玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.14,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,善治郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.68,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,他好了吗啾噜？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.27,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在过了东长崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.22,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,说是找到静留她爹了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.98,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,这个现在不重要！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.37,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,把关键的东西传达给她们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.69,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「再这样下去的话 世界会消失」？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:33.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「但是 可以将其逆转 让世界恢复原状」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,世界或许能恢复原状！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:44.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「去池袋 阻止7G的暴走 就有可能」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什么 是能轻易做到的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:47.21,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.18,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「正在调查方法」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「找到之后 就告诉帽帽帽」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.18,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,「帽帽帽帽」是什么意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:58.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他还是没法长时间对话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然正常的时间在延长就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.08,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,让世界变回去是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.12,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,在池袋做点什么就能变回人类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:09.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我也不知道 但是他之前说池袋是据点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.64,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,那我也和你们一起去啾噜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.15,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,那些戴帽子的可能还会来妨碍你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不来也没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.48,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,只有你们的话我会担心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:18.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还是人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:20.96,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,我也要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不来也行！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.97,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,这么重要的事怎么能交给女儿你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:27.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我只是去带叶香回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.51,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,世界可能无法变回原状哦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那种事我无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.67,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,啥——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎样都好啦！我无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:36.26,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,啾噜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.35,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事的 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留她很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.88,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,虽然可能是这样啦 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我能用弓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.62,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶头脑灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实有时候很疯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:50.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我会发狂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,性感暴力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.08,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起作为狼獾的时候 你现在要弱得多吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,更重要的是 你受伤了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,能让世界变回去的话 会让它变的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.74,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,这种轻浮的态度…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:04.53,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,千仓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.38,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,所谓女儿啊 就是会在两年内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:09.76,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,成长得超乎家长想象咻噼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.90,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,相信女儿 让她们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.10,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,我们首先应该做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:16.41,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,让身在吾野的家人们安心才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回去见妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,变成真正无法交谈的动物时就太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.77,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,确实 你有我亲传的吾野柔术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.10,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,应该能轻松解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:29.99,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:30.98,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,去吧 静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.92,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,为你的父亲复仇吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\pos(1437.333,1050.001)}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\pos(858.668,1050.001)}路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.04,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,{\pos(1840.001,1050.001)}谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.04,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,{\pos(1493.332,1050.001)}我知道的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:39.94,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,{\pos(1109.332,1050.001)}你们也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:47.33,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,加油啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:50.43,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,刚才你说的话 我好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:53.13,Default,Eisaku,0,0,0,,有家人在 就是这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.18,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.61,Default,Hide-bo,0,0,0,,荣作明明是个光棍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.94,Shizuru,Shizuru's Father,0,0,0,,好！该把人力工程车放回轨道上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.30,Default,Group,0,0,0,,遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:06.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,呀 静留你爸根本没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还是一样的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我觉得他很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:13.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 东吾野的线路没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,过不了的那部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,洪水肯定已经退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不行的话 总能想出办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:18.86,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真能吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我爸没问题的 虽然是笨蛋就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.08,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 我不是同意笨蛋的那部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我说啊 世界变回原状是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是字面意思吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:36.51,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就是变回7G之前的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:40.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然 我还是不知道哪边更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,虽然能变回去是好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但我已经放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,继续现在这样也挺轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我的游记在越来越混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:52.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.51,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,比起世界变回原状
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.41,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我更希望你和叶香重归于好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:00.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.21,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,再说了 就靠我们这几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么可能阻止7G的暴走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:10.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说不定某日某夜突然就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,觉醒了很了不得的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,唔 神圣的苦瓜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:25.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,聚集于我的身边 解放苦瓜之力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.72,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不是什么都没发生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你这骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:38.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊！ 还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你还我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:40.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,给我吐出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:42.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好 我这就吐出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,别吐出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不准吵架！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,醒醒 天气好像变糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉乌云像是在一瞬间涌了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,明明刚才天还是晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.90,0:13:03.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:03.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是椎名町站吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:05.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:09.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不停下来直接开走？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,毕竟静留的爸爸也说他们在这里被袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.04,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,直接开走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:14.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我去跟静留她们说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.62,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 你们醒了——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.12,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:31.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这根本去不了池袋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,唉 真不想下车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,绝对会遇见奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哪条路都无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我比我爸强多了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:46.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是很确定！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.63,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就不该期待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里根本没人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,连警察叔叔都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,茶碗蒸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:03.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的诶 茶碗蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:04.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.76,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,把人丢进茶碗里蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.84,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是五右卫门被拷问时的蒸刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:09.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,能不能别说这么吓人的—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:13.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么东西粘在我的脸上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋新闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.79,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这不是叶香吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs45\bord6.001\frz237.4\pos(1606.823,955.701)}出现阳光七十大道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs31.5\bord6.001\pos(1431.808,968.558)\frz249.2}好心办坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs36\bord6.001\frz269.7\pos(880.574,887.166)}{\fs40}{\an1}附近的探险队\N动身前往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs36\bord6.001\frz287.4\pos(651.534,924.232)}佛子的地藏生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord6.001\frz14.49\pos(512.312,872.233)}贡品被盗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs49.5\bord6.001\frz17.7\fs36\pos(1231.094,883.433)}毒太郎大人教给我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.97,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs49.5\bord6.001\fs27\pos(786.215,775.433)\frz350.3}行踪不明的丰岛园站\N发出救援信号了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}「三日凌晨」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:24.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「在天文学习课程中出席的中富叶香女王陛下」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:25.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}说是女王诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.00,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果她真的是叶香的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是不是比我记忆中的叶香要来得吓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,叛逆期？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,站在她旁边的人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,看上去长着一张坏人的脸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.98,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,莫非不想让这个世界复原的势力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.20,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,指的就是他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.10,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,你们几个！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.50,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,想去池袋是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.95,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们可不能让你们去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.27,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,就在这椎名町 把你们变成我们的作品吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？ 这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.05,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,变成他们的作品…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:57.69,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是说 给他们的作品当模特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.52,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,可能会把我们的衣服脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:00.72,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对我们做些色色的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,太坏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:02.74,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.334,1050.001)}咦 那顶帽子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他们多半就是干掉我爸爸的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等等 是不是有点像仙人地图上画的草饼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.16,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,啊！ 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:10.46,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,那顶贝雷帽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.04,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,那不是被奇怪的动物干掉的T氏的东西吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:13.64,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,给我还回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不还！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.30,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,呱！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.36,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,你们就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:20.14,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,糟蹋了我们在大泉学园之作的人吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:21.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,大泉学园？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是在说「练爱」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是 等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,也就是说把「练爱」的世界变得一团糟的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.50,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,正是在下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.48,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,爱丽丝的存在过于危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:34.38,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,那孩子的魅力甚至可能点燃池袋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,爱丽丝就是你害死的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:36.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.40,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,这是我的台词！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.96,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,剧画光束！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.01,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,根本就不像没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,变得好好有个性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.56,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有个性是什么意思？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我到底变成什么样了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:59.06,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,很快她的内在也会变成我们构思的角色！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,快把她变回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.21,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,我拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.43,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,只要离开这个城市 变化就会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.73,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,快回头吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:07.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不如用吾野柔术把你们揍一顿来得快！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.96,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,你能做得到吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.74,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,你们的连载将于此腰斩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你真敢做啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.36,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,看我把你们送往地狱！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.30,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,然后是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喏啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,变成这样要怎么使用柔术…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们必须保护好晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:28.00,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我会变成什么样的角色呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,如果要变的话 浮世绘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.31,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好像不错 但是我想要更前卫的角色 未来系的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.31,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,新连载开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:37.94,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,咳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:38.48,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:40.07,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,野兽派！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,立体主义！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:44.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,德式表现主义！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.15,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.49,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有什么东西出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:51.05,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,F氏！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:54.35,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,好可怕！好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.23,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.63,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.18,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,难道说 你们也得到了贝雷帽的力量？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,超现实轰炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:07.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 装出一副很懂的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,一下就看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他们说是贝雷帽的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有了这个说不定能战胜他们诺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:16.19,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,哼！我们漫画家绝不会让你们贫瘠的想象力得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.25,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.46,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.84,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,哈!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,见识了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:39.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,永远闷着头看书的晶的想象力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.40,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.15,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,一派胡言！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.51,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,你们做的一点都不王道！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:45.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊，晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.78,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,会如同你想象的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.15,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,BL闪光！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.33,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,F氏 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.01,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,别用那种眼神看我 A氏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.03,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,{\an8}F氏...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.02,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,啊啊这是什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:01.03,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,{\an8}A氏..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.84,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,不错！非常不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,闪光噗咻！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.32,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.05,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,突然觉得我不能待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.94,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,这种不被需要的感觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.77,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,哈 没有那种事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,热血火焰喏啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哔哔！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.88,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,哦！这样下去我们要输了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:21.95,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,一鼓作气决胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.07,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,做好觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.49,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,无论何地我都会追随你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.30,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,这种东西 我们不需要依靠它们！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.63,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.10,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,这展开太随便了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:34.64,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,亵渎！完全的亵渎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:37.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说到底为什么要妨碍我们喏啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们也有爱丽丝那所谓的魅力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.00,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,完全不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.06,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,接受了贝雷帽力量的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:45.89,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,必须要听从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.43,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,就只是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,接受了力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.73,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是怎么回事喏啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.65,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,看来不得不坦白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.65,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那种东西无所谓 只回答我们的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.97,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,那是多少年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叫你住嘴没听见吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:05.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs153\frz273.4\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2.25\pos(1689.181,641.988)}常盘庄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:02.94,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,我们胸怀大志 于此起步！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:04.71,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,用漫画给世界带来变革！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.89,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,但是 不知为何我们的画风不被接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.96,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,一点名声都没获得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:14.00,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,唯有光阴虚度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.64,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,故事情节必须是王道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.83,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,正是因为老套才令人动容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.97,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,但那群该死的编辑 嫌我们思想陈旧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.15,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,诶 怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:25.56,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,认真的？真的不听我们解释吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.09,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,回忆时段谁都不能行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.71,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,这样才算王道吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.51,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,我们还没讲到7G发生的时候呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.40,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,或者这份力量其实是付费订阅制的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.69,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,也没提到最重要的 是谁给的我们这份力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,即使如此也行得通 这般那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.97,Default,Group,0,0,0,,啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:41.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,表现是无限的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:51.24,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,纵使时代变迁 形形色色的东西被限制…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.25,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,全新的漫画的表现也会再次诞生！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.23,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,不如说是我们自己放弃了自己！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.02,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好像把他们点醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:20:00.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎样都好 好想赶紧变回原样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:01.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:02.92,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们认识这个孩子吗喏啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.66,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,你们真的是女王的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香是我们的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.96,0:20:10.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们现在要去见她诺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.31,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:15.07,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,你们这些小喽啰不可能轻易地见到她！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:18.48,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,女王可谓是现在的池袋之母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.21,Default,Tokiwaman F,0,0,0,,并且是给予我们力量的伟大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.67,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,你们的存在威胁了女王 乃至这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:29.32,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,毒太郎大人早就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毒太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:30.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.57,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,不就在那照片上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.62,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,旁边那个不那么高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毒太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.99,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,总之如果你们想活命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:40.50,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,最好别让女王感到不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.34,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,她会把你们变成茶碗蒸的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:47.35,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.601\fs99\fnArial Black\an7\c&H222523&\pos(231,317.999)}昨日的叛乱分子\N\N\N\N\N茶碗蒸
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们在派出所也看到了 那是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.33,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,就是字面意思！
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.33,0:20:47.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,果然 是拷问…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香才不会做那种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:52.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,毒太郎！我想起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎曾经提到过喏啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.10,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,毒太郎那个混账狗屎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.22,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,我都说了那么多次让他放弃7G了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就是他引发了7G事件喏啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香为什么和这种流氓在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我不知道诺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.02,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,薄德宰相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.40,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,烧鸡宰相？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:11.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:14.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也就是说 叶香是被那个人蒙蔽了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.10,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,或者说是被操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.87,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是 平时的叶香可不会相信那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,7G
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,受此影响是有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:27.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果是那样的话 就必须停止7G 没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那可真是莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,变回来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.79,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看上去是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.55,Default,Tokiwaman A,0,0,0,,那份力量契约 订阅被我们解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:43.25,Default,Tokiwawoman,0,0,0,,这东西超贵的 解除了也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:01.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.21,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋…
